The NewsLookout web scraping application for financial events.  Scalable, modular and configurable multi-threaded python console application. The application is readily extended by adding custom modules via its 'plugin' architecture for additional news sources,  custom data pre-processing and NLP based news text analytics  (e.g. entity recognition, negative event classification, economy trends, industry trends, etc.). For more details, refer to https://github.com/sandeep-sandhu/NewsLookout

